[SN]TITLE[SN]
Gang members banned from Birmingham's Ladywood

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Three brothers and a friend have been banned for two years from the area of Birmingham in which they live following the imposition of gang injunctions.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
Gang members Darryl Bishton, 24, along with Daman, 20, and 18-year-old Robert, may only go into Ladywood to get to their home on Guild Close.
Simieon Watson, 21, of Acorn Grove, Ladywood is subject to the same restriction.
If the four deviate from their route home, they could face prosecution.
